					<div class="KonaBody">
						<p>A first grade girl handed in the drawing below for a homework assignment.</p>
<p><img src="http://www.businesspundit.com/wp-content/uploads/2009/01/growup.jpg" alt="growup" title="growup" width="432" height="323" class="alignright size-full wp-image-8203" /></p>
<p>After it was graded and the child brought it home, she returned to school the next day with the following note:</p>
<p>Dear Ms. Davis,</p>
<p>I want to be very clear on my child&#8217;s illustration.  It is NOT of me on a dance pole on a stage in a strip joint.  I work at Home Depot and had commented to my daughter how much money we made in the recent snowstorm.  This photo is of me selling a shovel.</p>
<p>Mrs. Harrington</p>
